cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MS, cs.MM

This paper involves the use of deep learning techniques for image analysis and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of clinical demographics and integration of imaging data also suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of random forest classifier suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.MS) sub-category. Finally, the use of 3D attention-based deep convolutional neural net suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
